				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Only thing I don't approve of in this skip is Wondertainment's reaction to Scarf being taken. I just can't imagine the good doctor ever acting so serious and almost downright menacing.</p> </blockquote> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Spoilers?</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">hide</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p>Scarf's owner is not Wondertainment. It's some guy applied for a job with the doctor and now works for him.</p> </div> </div> </div> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1197130#post-2337412</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-1197130/scp-2991#post-2337412</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Mon, 13 Jul 2015 21:19:31 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Thekillerax</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1832151</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Only thing I don't approve of in this skip is Wondertainment's reaction to Scarf being taken. I just can't imagine the good doctor ever acting so serious and almost downright menacing. I am aware that there are many different interpretations and portrayals of Wondertainment, but their demeanor here contradicts everything that has been shown of their personality in other skips, and because of that I can't view agree with it at all. Other than that, this was very, very cute, and definitely worthy of an upvote. It's nice to see what happens to the toys that don't make it out of production.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
