				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2015 07:06:26 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Mulciber</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>300187</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Normally I find attempts at emotional manipulation in articles to be hamhanded and cheap. I read through this, moved on without voting, and then returned to it. Upon reading this section of the containment procedures again:</p> <blockquote> <p>Designated personnel are to remove SCP-2991 from containment for one hour every week to maintain continued responsiveness.</p> </blockquote> <p>I found myself slightly aghast at how little time that is to spend with a pet.</p> <p>You got me.</p> <p>+1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
